metadata.name: 8:23 AM
metadata.description:
It is very hard to go to school on days when el (#03) is not there.

Lee arrived at school alone, stopping at a convenience store to buy an energy drink, chasing stray cats, and wandering around aimlessly.

Miraculously, she makes it to school, but the shortest way to her classroom is blocked by construction on campus, and she is sure to be late.

She begins to feel her bass even heavier.
